{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["A Knight's Promise\n\n<size=45>Chapter 3 - I Found You, Commander!<\/size>",1]]},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"S- sorry...","dir":1,"side":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"effects":[{"active":true,"name":"memoryFog"}],"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I totally gave the thing to Akashi! But on my way back, I ran into U-81 playing with the girls and I kinda got caught up with them and forgot I was supposed to be working...","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But I definitely won't make that mistake again!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Oh yeah! Tomorrow's a day off so why don't you come play with us, Commander? You know working all the time is bad for you!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"And so thanks to U-556's weird apology-turned-invitation, I ended up going to U-81's hide-and-seek party.---","dir":1,"effects":[{"active":false,"name":"memoryFog"}],"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Okay, everybody come draw straws to decide who's \"it\"!","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":408010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"One... two...","actor":408040,"subActors":[{"actor":108010,"pos":{"x":555}},{"actor":308020,"pos":{"x":1125}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","dir":1},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ooh! It's me! I'm \"it\"!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":408040},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Heh heh. You just wait and see. I'll catch you all! 60, 59, 58...","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":408040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I thought carefully about where I should hide.","dir":1,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Go back to the office."},{"flag":2,"content":"Go with U-81."},{"flag":3,"content":"Hide right behind U-556's back."}],"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Nobody would ever think to hide the office. I decided that would be the safest place to stick it out.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","optionFlag":1},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"I made my way back to the office and quietly closed the door. Locking it would be against the rules, but I was already confident I had a perfect hiding spot.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","optionFlag":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"All I had to do was wait out the end of the game. Not to mention this was a great opportunity to get some work d-","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","optionFlag":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"*click click*","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","optionFlag":1},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I found you, Commander!","actor":408040,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"optionFlag":1,"effects":[{"active":true,"name":"speed"}],"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"MISSION FAILED.","dir":1,"effects":[{"active":false,"name":"speed"}],"bgName":"bg_story_task","optionFlag":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Oh, right. I had forgotten U-556 was my secretary ship and therefore...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","optionFlag":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I determined that U-81, hide and seek pro that she was, would no doubt have a masterful hiding spot.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","optionFlag":2},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"It turned out she wanted to hide... underwater!?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"star_level_bg_105","optionFlag":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I suppose it was only natural a submarine would want to hide underwater, but I found myself suffering certain limitations that meant...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"star_level_bg_105","optionFlag":2},{"expression":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I found you, Commander!","actor":408040,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"optionFlag":2,"effects":[{"active":true,"name":"speed"}],"bgName":"star_level_bg_105","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"MISSION FAILED.","dir":1,"effects":[{"active":false,"name":"speed"}],"bgName":"star_level_bg_105","optionFlag":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I determined that hiding in plain sight would be the best move. All I had to do was wait for U-556 to head off in search of the others, whereupon I would simply march up to the starting point and declare myself safe.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","optionFlag":3},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"20, 19, 18...","dir":1,"actorName":"U-556","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","optionFlag":3},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I just had to hold my breath long enough...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","optionFlag":3},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"2, 1, 0! Ready or not, here I come!","dir":1,"actorName":"U-556","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","optionFlag":3},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"......","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"actor":408040,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","optionFlag":3},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Commander? Did you think I wouldn't see you or what?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":408040,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","optionFlag":3},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"MISSION FAILED.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","optionFlag":3},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Thus ended the first round of hide-and-seek. Everyone gathered up once more.","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"So the only one U-556 could find was the Commander?","actor":408010,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"That's just because you guys had really good hiding spots!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":408040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I really don't think the bathhouse pool is that good of a hiding spot...","actor":308020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But why did she only find the Commander? And why so fast?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":108020},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... Hehehe. I'm thinking maybe you two have a special thing going, hmmmmm?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":108020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I ignored Albacore's taunt and readied myself for the second round. This time I was \"it\", and I was committed to showing these girls who ran this port!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"U556STORY3","fadeOut":1.5}